  ('optician-moex-02229', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一種隱形眼鏡的製造方式，品質較穩定且製造較簡單，常用來大量生產每日拋軟式隱形眼鏡？', '["車削法（lathe cutting）", "旋模法（spin casting）", "鑄模法（cast molding）", "混合法（combination）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "823ea7ba277e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "20080966bf93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02230', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Holden和Mertz（1984）的研究，日戴型軟式隱形眼鏡（daily wear, DW）與長戴型的軟式隱形眼鏡（extended wear, EW），要避免角膜水腫，其鏡片的傳氧率Dk/L（oxygen transmissibility, Dk/L），分別至少需達到？', '["16、45", "24、87", "32、120", "35、125"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "823ea7ba277e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "20080966bf93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-02231', 'optician', 'optician-moex-107-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關隱形眼鏡材質特性的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["離子性材料帶正電荷，非離子性材料表面不帶電荷", "鏡片抗張強度（tensile strength）越低，代表鏡片本身維持形狀的能力越佳", "矽水膠的彈性模數越高，鏡片較硬不易變形", "鏡片材質的濕潤角越大，鏡片越濕潤，戴起來越舒服"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "823ea7ba277e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "20080966bf93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
